name: Storefronts.Attributes
desc: The attributes for the storefronts resource.

items.name: defaultLanguageTag
items.desc: The default supported RFC4646 language tag for the storefront.

items.name: explicitContentPolicy
items.desc: Attribute indicating the level that this storefront can display explicit content.

items.name: name
items.desc: The localized name of the storefront.

items.name: supportedLanguageTags
items.desc: The supported RFC4646 language tags for the storefront.
